Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉  溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.03,0:00:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去溫泉嗎
