Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.65,0:23:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所失去的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.53,0:23:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待
